```plantuml
@startuml DehengYang_APRConfig

actor User
participant "Run_d4j_1.py" as RunScript
participant "Dataset/Defects4j.py" as Dataset
participant "Localization/Gzoltar.py" as Localizer
participant "Apr/SimFix.py" as APR
participant "Config.py" as Config
participant "Main_parse.py" as Parser

User -> RunScript: Execute script
RunScript -> Config: Load configuration
Config --> RunScript: Configuration data

RunScript -> Dataset: Load Defects4J dataset
Dataset --> RunScript: Buggy program data

RunScript -> Localizer: Perform fault localization
Localizer --> RunScript: Fault localization results

RunScript -> APR: Generate patches
APR --> RunScript: Candidate patches

RunScript -> Parser: Parse repair results
Parser --> RunScript: Formatted results (CSV)

@enduml
```